  02 Aug 2015; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> hspec-1.5.4.ebuild,
  hspec-1.7.2.1.ebuild, hspec-1.8.1.1.ebuild, hspec-1.8.3.ebuild:
  Drop dev-haskell/deepseq depend. ghc bundles it for a long while and we are
  using that version.

*hspec-2.1.4 (01 Aug 2015)

  01 Aug 2015; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +hspec-2.1.4.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  09 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> hspec-1.8.1.1.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #550402

  08 Jun 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> hspec-1.8.1.1.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #550402

*hspec-2.1.2 (13 Dec 2014)

  13 Dec 2014; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +hspec-2.1.2.ebuild:
  Bump hspec to 2.1.2

  25 Jul 2014; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Drop redundant '<maintainer>' field, leave only '<herd>'.

